@startuml
title Viaverse Badge / Review Prompt — State Diagram

[*] --> PROMPT_CREATED
PROMPT_CREATED --> PROMPT_SENT : notify
PROMPT_SENT --> REVIEW_SUBMITTED : user submits
PROMPT_SENT --> PROMPT_EXPIRED : timeout
REVIEW_SUBMITTED --> QUEUED_FOR_MODERATION : needs moderation
REVIEW_SUBMITTED --> REVIEW_PUBLISHED : auto safe
QUEUED_FOR_MODERATION --> REVIEW_PUBLISHED : approved
QUEUED_FOR_MODERATION --> REVIEW_REJECTED : rejected
REVIEW_PUBLISHED --> BADGE_ELIGIBLE : score/rule update
BADGE_ELIGIBLE --> BADGE_ACTIVE : award
BADGE_ACTIVE --> BADGE_REVOKED : criteria no longer met / admin
BADGE_REVOKED --> BADGE_ELIGIBLE : re-evaluate

PROMPT_EXPIRED --> [*]
REVIEW_REJECTED --> [*]

note bottom
Badges are not permanent trophies.
Trust/risk changes can revoke or downgrade them if criteria are no longer met.
end note
@enduml
